Subject: [MSN] Over 14,000 objects, artefacts and art works have been
	stolen from South Africa?s museums, galleries and heritage
	institutions in the last four years, the Democratic Alliance said on
	Friday.
To: <msn-list@te.verweg.com>
Message-ID: <0a8801c7aacc$2308d460$691a7d20$@org>
